name: JNZ: Nightmare Girls
summary: In this non-linear life sim, you get to play as a regular guy who has suddenly become a Catcher and must now chase and capture the demons in girls' subconscious using Jungian methods to save them from tragedy.

name: JNKPlat
summary: JNKPlat is a puzzle platformer for MS-DOS.

name: JNKPlat Slots
summary: JNKPlat slots sees the player spinning reels to that, when stopped, create an auto-controlled level for Platdude to attempt to complete.

name: JNKPlat 2018
summary: Guide Platdude through the various levels, as his continuing quest for the Spheres continues

name: JNKBombers
summary: JNKBombers is a Bomberman-style deathmatch game starring multiple characters from past Jayenkai titles.
